Apogee INDI Driver
==================

This package provides the INDI driver for Apgoee Alta U line of CCDs.

Requirtments
============

+ INDI >= v0.6 (http://indi.sf.net)

	You need to install both indi and indi-devel to build this package.
	
+ cfitsio

	cfitsio-devel is required to compile support for FITS.
	
+ libusb

	libusb-devel is required.
	
+ libapogee (http://indi.sf.net)

	
Installation
============

	See INSTALL
	
How to Use
==========

	You can use the Apogee Ulta INDI Driver in any INDI-compatible client such as KStars or Xephem. 
	
	To run the driver from the command line:
	
	$ indiserver indi_apogeeu_ccd
	
	You can then connect to the driver from any client, the default port is 7624.
	If you're using KStars, the driver will be automatically listed in KStars' Device Manager,
	no further configuration is necessary.
